    <section id="id1169728511409">
      <title>THE ROLE OF MEN AND WOMEN IN VARIOUS CULTURAL SITUATIONS</title>
      <para id="id1169719644448">Men, women, boys and girls, grandmothers and grandfathers play different roles at all the various cultural events in our South African society. Think of a wedding, christening or funeral that you attended recently.</para>
